review:
Very fun, I get to live out my oppressive slum lord fantasies. 

10/ 10 Way better than Ants and Legos.



Feedback: Some wall defenses like oil would be cool :}

for people who played "Age of Darkness: Final Stand" then you probably do not have to play the tutorial :D as the core game mechanic is the same :) 
runs really smooth and definitely in a good state for an EA Game :3

played one endless game, survived 63 days (till that point it was actually pretty easy) and after that i died almost instantly xD
